    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Lord,__ when____ Thou____ didst as-cend up-on the Cross,____ Thou didst ut--ter-ly___ o-blit-er-ate___ our an-ces-tral__ curse.__ And go-ing down in-to__ Ha---des, Thou didst_____ set free___ those in fet-ters from__ all__ ag-es__ past, grant-ing un---to the race of__ man__ in----cor-rup-tion for ev-er;__ hence, for this___ cause with hymns___ do we glo-ri--fy__ Thy life-cre-at-----ing and sav--ing__ Ris-ing from the__ dead.__"
    }
